Title: Ghost condensates in Yang-Mills theories in nonlinear gauges
Authors: A. R. Fazio and V. E. R. Lemes and M. Picariello and M. S. Sarandy and S. P. Sorella
Abstract: Ghost condensates of dimension two are analysed in a class of nonlinear gauges in pure Yang-Mills theories. These condensates are related to the breaking of the SL(2,R) symmetry, present in these gauges.
